headline.print_headline: Greek 2013 Fiscal Outcome May Be Better Than Expected
headline.main: Greek 2013 Fiscal Outcome May Be Better Than Expected

lead_paragraph: Debt-laden Greece may have achieved a better than expected fiscal outcome last year and might meet the conditions for further disbursements from international lenders in March, senior euro zone officials said on Monday.
